The idea is to save down the count of left parenthesis, then match it with double ')'.
If case of single ')' or end of String happened, we did special handling as shown below.

```
public int minInsertions(String s) {
        int res = 0, left = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == '(') { // when (
                left++;
            } else if (i == s.length() - 1 || s.charAt(i + 1) == '(') { // when single )
                if (left > 0) {
                    res++;
                    left--;
                } else {
                    res += 2;
                }
            } else { // when double )
                if (left > 0) left--;
                else res++;
                i++; // advance pointer since we have process double ) in a time
            }
        }
        res += left * 2;
        return res;
    }
