Erase adjucent same lower case and upper case laters every time by setting counter to 0.

# Approach
1. Loop through s.
2. If any adjuscent characters are similar lower case and upper case characters are same, erase them.
3. Set counter to -1, as we are increasing the counter every time in the loop.
4. At the end return the modified s.

