# Intuition
Store the running sum while traversing through the array.

# Approach
Prefix Sum, record the running sum and check if current (sum - target) already exists in the set. If it exists, it means that we found a subarray. Clear the values in the set (to avoid overlapping subarrays) and set the running sum to 0.Repeat the same process from the next element.

